cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a novel approach to document representation using recurrent neural network language models, which is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. Specifically, it is related to natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural networks (cs.NE).
